Author: cinnamonbicycle
Text: I can relate to this on so many levels. Watermelon is still a fear food for me lol. It's awful, I never wanted to get this bad but now I don't know if I want to fix it.

Author: Pyxxiss
Text: The moment I knew I was far gone was when I felt guilty for eating an unplanned cube of watermelon. It was literally the size of my thumb and I still get anxious thinking about it now.
